<!-- 2. EXECUTION ACTION PLAN -->
<section class="section" id="action-plan">
    <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-icon" style="background:#ecfdf5;">⚡</div>
        <div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Execution Action Plan</h2>
            <p class="section-desc">Immediate strategic moves to optimize performance and scale winning campaigns</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-title">🚀 Scale Winners</div>
            <span class="badge badge-scale">High Priority</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="action-list">
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num">1</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Increase Budget for "دنيا العيون 2026 — lazik"</h4>
                    <p>This campaign delivers messaging conversations at <strong>11.23 EGP</strong> — the best-performing lead gen ad set. Incrementally raise daily budget by <strong>15-20%</strong> every 3 days while monitoring cost stability.</p>
                    <div class="action-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">📈 Budget Scale</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">👁️ Eye World</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">⏱️ Start Immediately</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num">2</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Retarget "lasir" Engagers with Conversion Objective</h4>
                    <p>Top Care's "lasir" generated <strong>3,195 engagements at 1.12 EGP</strong> — but engagement ≠ revenue. Build a retargeting audience from these engagers and run <strong>"Messaging conversations"</strong> or <strong>"Lead Generation"</strong> ads to convert them into actual patient bookings.</p>
                    <div class="action-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">🎯 Retargeting</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">🦷 Top Care</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">⏱️ Within 48 Hours</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-title">🛠️ Fix Underperformers</div>
            <span class="badge badge-urgent">Critical</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="action-list">
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num" style="background:var(--danger);">1</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Pause "Teeth mssg2" Immediately</h4>
                    <p>Cost per result is <strong>60.59 EGP</strong> with only 2 conversations — this is burning budget with near-zero return. Pause today and redirect budget to "lasir" retargeting.</p>
                    <div class="action-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">🛑 Pause Now</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">🦷 Top Care</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num" style="background:var(--danger);">2</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Consolidate Governorate Campaigns</h4>
                    <p>"ليزك محافظات" campaigns (Giza, Fayoum, Beni Suef, Banha) have high costs (up to <strong>43.48 EGP</strong>) with tiny data. Merge into a single <strong>"Rest of Egypt"</strong> ad set to exit the learning phase faster and stabilize costs.</p>
                    <div class="action-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">🔀 Consolidate</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">👁️ Eye World</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-title">🔍 Review & Optimize</div>
            <span class="badge badge-review">This Week</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="action-list">
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num" style="background:var(--warning);color:#1e293b;">1</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>A/B Test Creatives for Expat Targeting</h4>
                    <p>"dr .ihab 2025" campaigns targeting Saudi Arabia, Libya, and Algeria cost <strong>26-30 EGP</strong> per conversation. Test new creatives tailored to <strong>medical tourism</strong> (Arabic-language, regional pricing, travel package visuals) to improve conversion from these regions.</p>
                    <div class="action-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">🧪 A/B Test</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">👁️ Eye World</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">🌍 Regional</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num" style="background:var(--warning);color:#1e293b;">2</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Revamp Dental Messaging Ads</h4>
                    <p>"Teeth mssg1" costs <strong>29.07 EGP</strong> — pause mssg2 first, then redesign mssg1 with: <strong>before/after photos</strong>, <strong>limited-time discount offers</strong>, or <strong>video patient testimonials</strong>. Test 3 new variations against current creative.</p>
                    <div class="action-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">🎨 Creative Refresh</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">🦷 Top Care</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- 3. CLEAR STEPS -->
<section class="section" id="steps" style="background:#f1f5f9;">
    <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-icon" style="background:#eff6ff;">📋</div>
        <div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Clear Steps — What Needs to Be Done</h2>
            <p class="section-desc">Day-by-day tactical checklist for the marketing team</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-title">Day 1 — Immediate Actions (Today)</div>
            <span class="badge badge-urgent">Do Now</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="action-list">
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num">1</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Pause "Teeth mssg2" Campaign</h4>
                    <p>Go to Ads Manager → Campaigns → Topcare → Teeth mssg2 → Toggle OFF. Reallocate its remaining budget to "lasir" retargeting campaign.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num">2</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Boost "دنيا العيون 2026 — lazik" Budget by 15%</h4>
                    <p>Edit ad set → Budget & Schedule → Increase daily budget. Set a calendar reminder to check cost per result in 72 hours.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num">3</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Create Retargeting Audience from "lasir" Engagers</h4>
                    <p>Audiences → Create Audience → Custom Audience → Engagement → People who engaged with any post or ad → Select "lasir" campaign → Name: "Top Care Lasir Engagers — 30D".</p>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-title">Day 2-3 — Campaign Restructure</div>
            <span class="badge badge-review">This Week</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="action-list">
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num">4</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Consolidate Governorate Campaigns into One Ad Set</h4>
                    <p>Pause individual governorate ad sets (Giza, Fayoum, Beni Suef, Banha). Create new ad set: <strong>"ليزك — محافظات مصر"</strong> with combined locations and existing winning creative. Set initial budget = sum of paused ad sets.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num">5</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Launch "lasir" Retargeting Campaign</h4>
                    <p>New campaign: Objective = <strong>Messages</strong>. Audience = "Top Care Lasir Engagers — 30D". Creative = booking-focused message ("Book your free consultation now"). Budget = 500 EGP/day initially.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num">6</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Duplicate "Teeth mssg1" with 3 New Creative Variations</h4>
                    <p>Variation A: Before/after carousel. Variation B: Limited-time 20% discount + countdown. Variation C: 30-second patient testimonial video. Keep same targeting, run for 5 days, then evaluate.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-title">Day 4-7 — Testing & Monitoring</div>
            <span class="badge badge-general">Ongoing</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="action-list">
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num">7</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Launch Expat A/B Test for "dr .ihab 2025"</h4>
                    <p>Duplicate the campaign twice. Ad Set A = current creative. Ad Set B = new creative with medical tourism angle (Arabic copy, package pricing, hospital accreditation badges). Run for 7 days with equal budget split.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="action-item">
                <span class="action-num">8</span>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <h4>Set Up CRM Tracking for Conversation Quality</h4>
                    <p>Work with sales team to tag every messaging lead source = Facebook Ads. Track: (1) Conversation → Appointment booked, (2) Appointment → Showed up, (3) Showed up → Paid procedure. Calculate true ROAS by campaign.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="action-item">
